import React from 'react';
import { ChakraProvider, Box, Grid, GridItem, Heading, Text, Radio, RadioGroup,Input, Button, Container, Flex, FormControl, FormLabel, Image } from '@chakra-ui/react';
import { LockIcon, EmailIcon } from '@chakra-ui/icons';
import { FaSun, FaMoon, FaUndo } from "react-icons/fa";


const AdminLoginPage = () => {
  return (
    <ChakraProvider>
      <Box minHeight="100vh" bgGradient="linear(to-t, teal.200, teal.300)">



        {/* Header */}
        <Box py={4} color="white">
          <Container maxW="container.lg">
            <Flex alignItems="center" justifyContent="space-between">
              {/* <Image src="/logo.svg" alt="Logo" boxSize="50px" /> */}
              <Heading size="lg">Admin Login</Heading>
            </Flex>
          </Container>
        </Box>
        

 
        {/* --------------------------------------------------------------------------------- */}
       
    <Container maxW="container.lg" py={3}>
      <Heading as="h1" mb={6}>Home Page</Heading>
      
      {/* Cards Section */}
      <Flex flexWrap="wrap" justifyContent="space-between">
        {/* Card 1 */}
        <Box flex="0 0 23%" mb={4}>
          <Box bg="white" boxShadow="md" borderRadius="md" p={4}>
            <Heading as="h5" fontSize="sm" mb={2}>Users</Heading>
            <Heading as="h2" fontSize="xl" mb={2}>10</Heading>
            <Image src="/assets/img/banner/1.png" alt="" />
          </Box>
        </Box>

        {/* Card 2 */}
        <Box flex="0 0 23%" mb={4}>
          <Box bg="white" boxShadow="md" borderRadius="md" p={4}>
            <Heading as="h5" fontSize="sm" mb={2}>Departments</Heading>
            <Heading as="h2" fontSize="xl" mb={2}>5</Heading>
            <Image src="/assets/img/banner/2.png" alt="" />
          </Box>
        </Box>

        {/* Card 3 */}
        <Box flex="0 0 23%" mb={4}>
          <Box bg="white" boxShadow="md" borderRadius="md" p={4}>
            <Heading as="h5" fontSize="sm" mb={2}>Designations</Heading>
            <Heading as="h2" fontSize="xl" mb={2}>8</Heading>
            <Image src="/assets/img/banner/3.png" alt="" />
          </Box>
        </Box>

        {/* Card 4 */}
        <Box flex="0 0 23%" mb={4}>
          <Box bg="white" boxShadow="md" borderRadius="md" p={4}>
            <Heading as="h5" fontSize="sm" mb={2}>Roles</Heading>
            <Heading as="h2" fontSize="xl" mb={2}>12</Heading>
            <Image src="/assets/img/banner/4.png" alt="" />
          </Box>
        </Box>
      </Flex>
    </Container>
  );
}


       
       
       
       
       
       
       
       
       
       
       
       
       
        {/* --------------------------------------------------------------------------------- */}
        {/* Main Content */}
        <Flex>
          {/* Left Menu */}
          <GridItem colSpan={0.55} bg="gray" p={50} borderRadius="md" h={900}>
            <Heading size="md" mb={2}></Heading> {/* Increase mb value here */}
            <Box p={1}>
              <Box mb={10} bg="blue.100" borderRadius="md" width="100%" maxW="300px">
                <Text p={4}>Dashboard</Text> {/* Apply padding to adjust spacing */}
              </Box>
              <Box mb={10} bg="gray.200" borderRadius="md" display="inline-block" width="100%">
                <Text p={4}>Seller Tool</Text> {/* Apply padding to adjust spacing */}
              </Box>
              <Box mb={10} bg="blue.100" borderRadius="md" display="inline-block" width="100%">
                <Text p={4}>BuyLeads</Text> {/* Apply padding to adjust spacing */}
              </Box>
              <Box mb={10} bg="gray.200" borderRadius="md" display="inline-block" width="100%">
                <Text p={4}>Settings</Text> {/* Apply padding to adjust spacing */}
              </Box>
            </Box>
          </GridItem>

          {/* Card */}
          <GridItem colSpan={0.45}>
            <Box bg="gray.200" p={8} borderRadius="md" height="400px"> {/* Adjust the height here */}
           <Heading size="md" mb={4}>Card 1</Heading>
               <Text>This is the content of the card.</Text>
             </Box>
          </GridItem>
          <GridItem colSpan={0.45}>
            <Box bg="Background" p={8} borderRadius="md" height="400px">
              <Heading size="md" mb={4}>Card 2</Heading>
              <Text>This is the content of the card.</Text>
            </Box>
          </GridItem>
          <GridItem colSpan={0.45}>
            <Box bg="gray.200" p={8} borderRadius="md" height="400px">
              <Heading size="md" mb={4}>Card 3</Heading>
              <Text>This is the content of the card.</Text>
            </Box>
          </GridItem>
          <GridItem colSpan={0.45}>
            <Box bg="Background" p={8} borderRadius="md" height="400px">
              <Heading size="md" mb={4}>Card 4</Heading>
              <Text>This is the content of the card.</Text>
            </Box>
          </GridItem>
        </Flex>

        {/* Footer */}
        <Box py={4} bg="white" color="teal" mt={4}>
          <Container maxW="container.lg">
            <Flex justifyContent="center">
              <Text>Â© 2024 Nixcel Software Pvt.Ltd All rights reserved.</Text>
            </Flex>
          </Container>
        </Box>
      </Box>
    </ChakraProvider>
  );
};

export default AdminLoginPage;
